# Input

```css
div:not(
    :last-child
    ) {
}

:not(
    div 
    
    +
     #id:hover
     
     ) {}

input:not(:where([type='submit'], [type='checkbox'], [type='radio'], [type='button'], [type='reset'])) {
	inline-size: 100%;
}

```


# Formatted

```css
div:not(:last-child) {
}

:not(div + #id:hover) {
}

input:not(
	:where(
		[type="submit"],
		[type="checkbox"],
		[type="radio"],
		[type="button"],
		[type="reset"]
	)
) {
	inline-size: 100%;
}

```
